ActCanada National Parks Act

Migratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
SubjectMigratory Birds Regulations
PrecisMIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS, 2022 in order to (1) clarify provisions, meet current legal drafting standards, and reorganize information; (2) recognize Aboriginal and treaty harvesting rights according to section 35 of the Constitution Act, 1982; and (3) introduce new provisions on migratory game bird hunting.
